  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Limoria</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A single-player psychological horror game. In this experience set in an old and mysterious hotel, you explore constantly shifting spaces that challenge the limits of your mind. Each time you wake up, the hotel and its surroundings change, confronting you with disturbing and strange occurrences. As the player, you gather clues within the depths of the atmosphere and try to understand the mystery behind the crumbling reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore Your Surroundings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This psychological horror is filled with elements that cloud your vision with each discovery. The game doesn’t hand you the story directly; to understand it, you must immerse yourself in the atmosphere and pay attention to clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/101d7559550a41439c7ef57b0c422c3e.poster.avif?t=1768336411\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/101d7559550a41439c7ef57b0c422c3e.webm?t=1768336411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/101d7559550a41439c7ef57b0c422c3e.mp4?t=1768336411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find Your Way Out of a Fractured Mind</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With each level, the protagonist’s mind will deteriorate further. Discover the exit and witness even more mysteries in the process.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/cd5cd85bfec3dbc7b65eb54ffd8cc8eb.poster.avif?t=1768336411\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/cd5cd85bfec3dbc7b65eb54ffd8cc8eb.webm?t=1768336411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/cd5cd85bfec3dbc7b65eb54ffd8cc8eb.mp4?t=1768336411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You Can Escape Anything but Not Your Memories</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the game, your memories will follow you; even if you’d rather not see them, you’ll pay the price of their consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/05f11ef4c219604f56c4bce268f76dd1.poster.avif?t=1768336411\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/05f11ef4c219604f56c4bce268f76dd1.webm?t=1768336411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/05f11ef4c219604f56c4bce268f76dd1.mp4?t=1768336411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Walking Simulation</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Realistic Graphics</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>High-Quality Sounds</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Environmental Changes</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“Do you want to escape, or do you want to uncover all the secrets? Which reality are you ready to face?”</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Limoria</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A single-player psychological horror game. In this experience set in an old and mysterious hotel, you explore constantly shifting spaces that challenge the limits of your mind. Each time you wake up, the hotel and its surroundings change, confronting you with disturbing and strange occurrences. As the player, you gather clues within the depths of the atmosphere and try to understand the mystery behind the crumbling reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore Your Surroundings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This psychological horror is filled with elements that cloud your vision with each discovery. The game doesn’t hand you the story directly; to understand it, you must immerse yourself in the atmosphere and pay attention to clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/101d7559550a41439c7ef57b0c422c3e.poster.avif?t=1768336411\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/101d7559550a41439c7ef57b0c422c3e.webm?t=1768336411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/101d7559550a41439c7ef57b0c422c3e.mp4?t=1768336411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find Your Way Out of a Fractured Mind</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With each level, the protagonist’s mind will deteriorate further. Discover the exit and witness even more mysteries in the process.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/cd5cd85bfec3dbc7b65eb54ffd8cc8eb.poster.avif?t=1768336411\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/cd5cd85bfec3dbc7b65eb54ffd8cc8eb.webm?t=1768336411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/cd5cd85bfec3dbc7b65eb54ffd8cc8eb.mp4?t=1768336411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You Can Escape Anything but Not Your Memories</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the game, your memories will follow you; even if you’d rather not see them, you’ll pay the price of their consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/05f11ef4c219604f56c4bce268f76dd1.poster.avif?t=1768336411\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/05f11ef4c219604f56c4bce268f76dd1.webm?t=1768336411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351140/extras/05f11ef4c219604f56c4bce268f76dd1.mp4?t=1768336411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Walking Simulation</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Realistic Graphics</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>High-Quality Sounds</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Environmental Changes</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“Do you want to escape, or do you want to uncover all the secrets? Which reality are you ready to face?”</i></p>",
